This is just here for when you cant be bothered to make your own skybox or figure out how.

Just place this file into the prefabs folder in

sourcedk > bin > prefabs

and insert as prefab when in hammer, easy :D

(I have set the skybox and light environment to de_tides to change it you must use these figure in the light_environment options.

Found at http://www.fpsbanana.com/tuts/254
